same PNPid (SGX0200), so ddccontrol can't distinguish between each
monitor.

I also think SGI GDM-5411 CAPS string is invalid, but I need to be sure
it is not a bug in ddccontrol. Could you please run this command on the
GDM-5411 :
# ./ddccontrol -p -v -v -c

Thanks,

Best regards,

Nicolas

